description: Services on the Douglas-Heysham and Douglas-Liverpool routes are cancelled.
title: Storm Ellen: Gales lead to Isle of Man-England ferry cancellations
title_page: Storm Ellen: Gales lead to Isle of Man-England ferry cancellations - BBC News
maintext: Ronaldsway Met Office said heavy rain and gusts of up to 90km (55mph) were expected throughout the morning, which could "lead to damage to anything not tied down, such as garden furniture".
